reviewText: Not one single bit of nudity in either film.

STEPHANIE BEATON is Perfectly Cast in DEREK & BRIAN ZEMRAK's "Bikini Planet"; for Her Exquisite Beauty & Unparalleled Bikini-Clad Body are Definitely Out-Of-This-World ! She also Displays Extraordinary Comedic Skills as "Princess Nibi" ! Ms. Beaton could carry this light-hearted  Comedy alone ; but She has a Great Supporting Cast of Young Nymphs ! Among them are LISA LOWE, ANGIE WARRINGTON, VANESSA ROSS,  JACKLYN LICK, & KATHERYN HECHT as Mean-Spirited "Queen Numnum" !
  B-Movie Icon, CONRAD BROOKS, has a Great Cameo as the "Vice-President" for "President Bubba Shrub", portrayed with Comedic Flair by RICHARD VAN FLEET ! LUIGI FRANCIS SHORTY ROSSI is a Must-See as a Diminutive Lady-Pleaser "Jerome" !
  "Bikini Planet" is a Fabulous No-Think Farce that is Perfect to just Sit Back, Relax, & Enjoy !!
Hmmm, Did I mention STEPHANIE BEATON???!!!
poorly made, not interesting, silly plot, poor acting
Rubbish! If you're looking for modern attempts at oldies science fiction buy Christopher R. Mihm's films instead!
